v.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/KSHM/111%2c%e8%81%b2%2c468%2c20220502%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"KSHM,111,聲,468,20220502,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"468","JDATE":"20220502","JTITLE":"聲請定其應執行刑"}